    {
      "id": "PopularPost235131",
      "post_content": "This is a pretty bad pump. It's a glorified [Giant Growth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth) costing 2 mana more. Sure it does grant you flying, so your creature has a chance to go through for some damage, but it's a sorcery so surprising your opponent and potentially taking out a bigger creature is out of the window.\n  \n   \nPlay [Giant Growth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth) and it's kin if you need a good pump, try something like [Distortion Strike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Distortion Strike) if you care about your creatures going through unblocked. And if you really want to spend 3 mana in white just play another creature.\n  \n   \n1/5",
      "posted_by": "Infini-",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost235131\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">This is a pretty bad pump. It's a glorified <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Giant Growth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth\">Giant Growth</a> costing 2 mana more. Sure it does grant you flying, so your creature has a chance to go through for some damage, but it's a sorcery so surprising your opponent and potentially taking out a bigger creature is out of the window.\r<br/> <br/>Play <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Giant Growth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth\">Giant Growth</a> and it's kin if you need a good pump, try something like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Distortion Strike\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Distortion Strike\">Distortion Strike</a> if you care about your creatures going through unblocked. And if you really want to spend 3 mana in white just play another creature.\r<br/> <br/>1/5</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '235131'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80544\">Infini-</span>\r\n                                (3/29/2012 2:06:05 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
