    {
      "id": "PopularPost266444",
      "post_content": "@Infini- [Giant Growth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth) isn't really a pump spell. It's a combat trick because, it's an instant and costs ![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol). This is a sorcery that costs ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![White](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=W&type=symbol), it can't be used to turn the tides of combat. Also, [Distortion Strike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Distortion Strike) is in blue, the color of evasion. While this is a really bad spell, you shouldn't compare it to cards from other colors, that's just unfair because white does not fill the role that either green or blue does. Each color has unique advantages and disadvantages.",
      "posted_by": "Ligerman30",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost266444\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">@Infini- <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Giant Growth\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Giant Growth\">Giant Growth</a> isn't really a pump spell.  It's a combat trick because, it's an instant and costs <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/>.  This is a sorcery that costs <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"White\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=W&amp;type=symbol\"/>, it can't be used to turn the tides of combat. Also, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Distortion Strike\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Distortion Strike\">Distortion Strike</a> is in blue, the color of evasion. While this is a really bad spell, you shouldn't compare it to cards from other colors, that's just unfair because white does not fill the role that either green or blue does.  Each color has unique advantages and disadvantages.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '266444'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy82380\">Ligerman30</span>\r\n                                (9/5/2012 12:02:52 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
