    {
      "id": "PopularPost307437",
      "post_content": "1. It's Portal! There -weren't- any instants to fool around with, and only cards like [Mystic Denial](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mystic Denial) and [Extinguish](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Extinguish) could've touched this. I imagine that this was pretty darned strong for the time.  \n  \n2. Say we lived in a non-Portal world. This still turns your mana dorks into 4/4 fliers, forcing your opponent to think about, \"Geez, do I want the 2-for-1 or is his other threat on the board still just going to murder me?\"  \n  \n3.5 in the weird land known as Portal, 2.5 as a card I think would be reasonable to see again for a draft format one of these days.",
      "posted_by": "WokeUpDead",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost307437\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">1. It's Portal! There -weren't- any instants to fool around with, and only cards like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mystic Denial\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mystic Denial\">Mystic Denial</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Extinguish\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Extinguish\">Extinguish</a> could've touched this. I imagine that this was pretty darned strong for the time.<br/><br/>2. Say we lived in a non-Portal world. This still turns your mana dorks into 4/4 fliers, forcing your opponent to think about, \"Geez, do I want the 2-for-1 or is his other threat on the board still just going to murder me?\"<br/><br/>3.5 in the weird land known as Portal, 2.5 as a card I think would be reasonable to see again for a draft format one of these days.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '307437'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy7771\">WokeUpDead</span>\r\n                                (4/7/2013 7:35:54 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                               